             <https://w3id.org/finos/cdm/DividendDateReferenceEnum#CumulativeEquityExDiv>
             <https://w3id.org/finos/cdm/DividendDateReferenceEnum#CumulativeEquityPaid>
             <https://w3id.org/finos/cdm/DividendDateReferenceEnum#CumulativeEquityExDivBeforeReset>
             <https://w3id.org/finos/cdm/DividendDateReferenceEnum#CumulativeEquityPaidBeforeReset>
             <https://w3id.org/finos/cdm/DividendDateReferenceEnum#CumulativeEquityPaidInclReset>
