          <ratedParty> [ <https://w3id.org/finos/cdm/RatedPartyEnum#Party>
             <https://w3id.org/finos/cdm/RatedPartyEnum#CreditSupportProvider>
             <https://w3id.org/finos/cdm/RatedPartyEnum#NamedEntity>
